HOW IT BEGAN


21 Feb 2019 15:58





This bad boy is a big, mean, luau party machine!

⇢⇠

⇣⇣




How this actually became a thing can only be explained by the collective insanity of four madmen.

Co-written by: DrAnnoyingDog

⇢⇠

⇣⇣


This was literally an idea that popped up out of no where. I was sitting at work and I think I was just kinda mulling over how much I hated cleaning the pool when I was a kid (I grew up in Florida.) And then the image above just sorta happened.

Outside of the initial concept, I wrote the containment as well as the containment attempts. Also did a few edits to try and tie each section together.

Overall, it's a pretty goofy SCP. It could very easily be a -j if we had wanted to go in that direction. But we wanted to just write something fun, silly, and enjoyable to read. It's probably not for everyone but I hope you enjoy regardless!








